# Compiled TypeScript output (built by `go generate ./...` locally and
# the Dockerfile build stage in prod). Sources of truth live under
# static-src/. The CSS bundle (static/style.css) IS committed and the
# drift check in scripts/validate-local.sh enforces it stays in sync
# with static-src/css/MANIFEST — re-run `go generate ./...` after
# editing the CSS sources.
static/*.js
static/wire/
node_modules/

